dc_title_s: C-22 Geologic Atlas of Chisago County, Minnesota [Part A]
dc_description_s: 6 pls. Scales 1:100,000 and 1:200,000. Pl. 1, data-base map; pl. 2, bedrock geology; pl. 3, surficial geology; pl. 4 Quaternary stratigraphy; pl. 5, sand distribution model and Precambrian bedrock geology; pl. 6, bedrock topography, and depth to bedrock. Supplementary files include ArcGis coverages, shapefiles and/or ESRI grids used to construct the plates, and metadata.; Surface and subsurface geology of Chisago County
